表的代码预览采购

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('collect') and o.name = 'FK_COLLECT_COLLECT_ENTERPRI')
alter table collect
drop constraint FK_COLLECT_COLLECT_ENTERPRI
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('collect') and o.name = 'FK_COLLECT_COLLECT2_MEDICINE')
alter table collect
drop constraint FK_COLLECT_COLLECT2_MEDICINE
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('collect')
and name = 'collect2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index collect.collect2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('collect')
and name = 'collect_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index collect.collect_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('collect')
and type = 'U')
drop table collect
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: collect */
/*==============================================================*/
create table collect (
eno char(8) not null,
mno char(10) not null,
constraint PK_COLLECT primary key nonclustered (eno, mno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: collect_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index collect_FK on collect (
eno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: collect2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index collect2_FK on collect (
mno ASC
)
go

alter table collect
add constraint FK_COLLECT_COLLECT_ENTERPRI foreign key (eno)
references enterprise (eno)
go

alter table collect
add constraint FK_COLLECT_COLLECT2_MEDICINE foreign key (mno)
references medicine (mno)
go
